name: 10000+ Icon Library Components Set
description:
The icon library is a delightful, beautifully executed symbols for common actions and objects.


Icons from open libraries that you can easily add to your web project from repositories:

  • bootstrapicons
  • boxicons
  • iconsax
  • jamicons
  • and others


Save yourself a library of icons to use in your digital products for mobile apps and websites.


Recommended for use as a command library. All icons have been converted to components.


Get inspired, created and delight customers! And follow me :)
